<p class="">The whole question of group libel—and that is what this really is—is a matter which has been engaging the attention of distinguished lawyers recently. I do not think they have found any satisfactory solution to it, and I am sure the House would not expect me, as a layman, to pronounce upon so intricate and legalistic a point.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
